General.Name: Freemelt Holding AB
General.Description: Freemelt Holding AB (publ), through its subsidiaries, engages in the metal 3D-printing business primarily in Europe and North America. The company offers Freemelt ONE, an electron beam-based 3D printer for research and development. It serves universities, research institutes, and research and development departments in large enterprises. The company was incorporated in 2017 and is headquartered in Mölndal, Sweden.
